					</div>
				</header><main id="primary" class="site-main">
	<article id="149288" class="cpt entretien single ">
    <div class="header floating-legend-container">

        <div class="infos entretien-infos">

            <h1 class="field-title">Entretien avec Pierre Bourgault</h1>
            <h2 class="field-subtitle"></h2>

                                <a href="https://esse.ca/auteurs/dominique-allard/">
                    <div class="field-author">

                        Dominique Allard                    </div>
                </a>
    
                
            <div class="tags tags-2">
                <a class='tag-link' href="https://esse.ca/categorie/entretien/">
                <span class="tag">Entretien</span>
            </a>
                <a class='tag-link' href="https://esse.ca/categorie/compte-rendu/webzine/">
                <span class="tag">Webzine</span>
            </a>
                <a class='tag-link' href="https://esse.ca/artistes/pierre-bourgault/">
                <span class="tag">Pierre Bourgault</span>
            </a>
    
</div>            <div class="field-excerpt">
                            </div>
            <div class="partage">
    <div class="shared-counts-wrap shortcode style-icon"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://esse.ca/entretien/entretien-avec-pierre-bourgault/&amp;display=popup&amp;ref=plugin&amp;src=share_button" title="Share on Facebook"  target="_blank"  rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"  class="shared-counts-button facebook shared-counts-no-count" data-postid="149288" data-social-network="Facebook" data-social-action="Share" data-social-target="https://esse.ca/entretien/entretien-avec-pierre-bourgault/"><span class="shared-counts-icon-label"><span class="shared-counts-icon"><svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18.8125" height="32" viewBox="0 0 602 1024"><path d="M548 6.857v150.857h-89.714q-49.143 0-66.286 20.571t-17.143 61.714v108h167.429l-22.286 169.143h-145.143v433.714h-174.857v-433.714h-145.714v-169.143h145.714v-124.571q0-106.286 59.429-164.857t158.286-58.571q84 0 130.286 6.857z"></path></svg></span><span class="shared-counts-label">Facebook</span></span></a><a href="https://twitter.com/share?url=https://esse.ca/entretien/entretien-avec-pierre-bourgault/&amp;text=Entretien%20avec%20Pierre%20Bourgault" title="Share on Twitter"  target="_blank"  rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"  class="shared-counts-button twitter shared-counts-no-count" data-postid="149288" data-social-network="Twitter" data-social-action="Tweet" data-social-target="https://esse.ca/entretien/entretien-avec-pierre-bourgault/"><span class="shared-counts-icon-label"><span class="shared-counts-icon"><svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="29.71875" height="32" viewBox="0 0 951 1024"><path d="M925.714 233.143q-38.286 56-92.571 95.429 0.571 8 0.571 24 0 74.286-21.714 148.286t-66 142-105.429 120.286-147.429 83.429-184.571 31.143q-154.857 0-283.429-82.857 20 2.286 44.571 2.286 128.571 0 229.143-78.857-60-1.143-107.429-36.857t-65.143-91.143q18.857 2.857 34.857 2.857 24.571 0 48.571-6.286-64-13.143-106-63.714t-42-117.429v-2.286q38.857 21.714 83.